Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.54,0:01:44.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:102540,104042}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:45.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:104042,105251}Good morning, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:46.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:105251,106502}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:48.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:106502,108796}Good morning. It's getting\Nso cold these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:51.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108796,111716}Of course it is.\NChristmas is almost here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:54.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111716,114886}Christmas.\NWouldn't it be nice if it snowed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:56.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114886,116179}It certainly would.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:00.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116179,120183}Has anybody noticed how quiet\Nthe class has gotten lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:05.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:123186,125146}And the reason is right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.43,0:02:06.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125438,126898}Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.89,0:02:10.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:126898,130693}He hasn't received any notes\Nfrom St. Tail lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:12.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:130693,132612}And that's why\Nhe's been down in the dumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:16.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133071,136866}I understand how he feels.\NHe misses the chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:21.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:137700,141579}Is that why he's so gloomy?\NHow silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:24.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142705,144957}Cheer up, Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:29.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146584,149545}Oh. It's only you, Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:30.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149796,150963}{\i1}How rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:34.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:151339,154801}So what if St. Tail doesn't appear?\NIt only proves the world is at peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:36.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154801,156260}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:40.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157136,160098}How can you jabber so much\Nfirst thing in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:42.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160098,162225}That's why I can't stand\Nthe girls in this class.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:44.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162517,164310}What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:47.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164310,167980}You're all nosy, loud-mouthed\Nand unfeminine on top of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:53.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170775,173236}Okay, then tell me\Nwhat's your ideal girl like, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:54.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173236,174445}Come on, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:57.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174946,177198}It's not you, that's for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:03:00.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177198,180451}There's no such thing\Nas the perfect girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:03.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180451,183162}Yes, there is!\NTake St. Tail, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:10.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187041,190878}What's wrong with you?\NIt's always St. Tail, St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:13.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193089,193881}Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:19.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198511,199512}Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:23.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200304,203850}You moron!\NI hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:30.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206227,210815}{\i1}I'm St. Tail.\NAnd if I'm her, then why…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:40.45,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:217405,220450}Surprise!\NThe Large Lizard Santa Claus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:59.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234213,239343}Mayu, isn't it?\NThere's no one here but me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:00.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239343,240720}You can tell me your problem now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:05.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241471,245683}Sister, Goh stole Tama from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245975,247226}Goh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:10.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247226,250980}He's in my class and he's so mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:15.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250980,255401}I'm not even bothering him, but he kicks\Nmy blocks and hits me with the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:18.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255401,258529}And he's the one\Nwho stole your pet, Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:19.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258529,259447}Uh huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:22.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260615,262533}Did you tell your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:29.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263785,269457}But Mama hates animals.\NShe said he should keep Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:30.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269457,270416}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:33.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271876,273669}I really love Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:38.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273669,278216}I understand. Don't cry.\NI'm sure God will help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:39.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278633,279717}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283805,285014}And that's the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:49.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285515,289393}Goh is really Gouta Ogasawara.\NHe's five years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:51.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289393,291604}And he lives on the hill\Non the outskirts of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:53.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292146,293940}And what does Tama look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:58.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294649,298152}She's black in color and\Nhas a ribbon around her neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:00.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298152,300571}I think she'll be easy to spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:04.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300571,304075}Alright. I guess I'll go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:07.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304534,307328}Wait, what about a\Nnote to Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:10.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:307954,310873}Forget it.\NWho cares about that promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:13.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310873,313793}That means\Nyou'll be breaking the promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:15.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314710,315419}I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:18.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317296,318422}Meimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:24.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:319507,324887}He only thinks of St. Tail! I'm not sending\Nanother note to that guy. Not ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:34.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331435,334146}The bully's room\Nshould be underneath me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:51.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350496,351914}{\i1}Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:57.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355668,357461}So you're the little meany.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:01.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358337,361632}You'd better start\Nthinking about how girls feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:05.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362592,365511}Or you'll end up like\Na certain blockhead I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:13.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:370850,373227}{\i1}Phew. Gee, I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:15.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373227,375563}{\i1}Now, where's that Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:23.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379567,383946}Here Tama… Oh, Tama…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:41.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398085,401756}{\i1}Black in color,\Nwith a ribbon. It can't be, can it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:47.76,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:401756,407762}Tama
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:47.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402632,407762}{\i1}Are you Tama? I thought you'd\Nbe a cute little black cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:58.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415436,418522}{\i1}What'll I do?\NI'm too scared to touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:01.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418522,421400}{\i1}Which means I can't steal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:02.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421400,422735}{\i1}This is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:04.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422735,424946}{\i1}My reputation is at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:24.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441545,444882}Tama, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:36.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455267,456394}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:40.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457603,460856}I'll call it quits for tonight.\NI've got to get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:46.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464652,466487}Detective Asuka, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:49.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468364,469281}After her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469824,471784}It's St. Tail! After her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:55.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474078,475287}Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486048,487717}We've got her cornered now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:09.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488342,489719}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:19.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497893,499729}I warned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:24.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503357,504442}Oh, damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:27.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506569,507278}Detective Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:29.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508154,509071}Don't hang on to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509071,510656}I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:31.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510656,511323}Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:35.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511323,515244}– Don't do that, sir!\N– Help, I'm sinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:39.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517079,519790}St. Tail appears!\NBut what is her target?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:41.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519790,521751}The mystery thickens!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:46.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523294,526213}Detective Asuka\Nmisses the arrest by an inch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:49.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526672,529383}It's been pretty long\Nsince St. Tail's last caper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:53.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529383,533512}I heard your Dad came close\Nto capturing her this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:54.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:533512,534930}Isn't that right, Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:58.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534930,538726}Shut up!\NShe never sent me a note!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:00.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538726,540770}That's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:03.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540770,543022}Who does she think\Nshe's dealing with, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:04.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543022,544690}Calm down, Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:08.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545441,548027}I was waiting for a note!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:10.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548027,550654}Why'd she do it\Nwithout letting me know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:13.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550946,553657}What'll I do?\NIt's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:19.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554158,559497}Cheer up. I'm sure she just\Nforgot her promise to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:23.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559497,563125}She's not like that!\NShe'd never break her promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:25.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563125,565252}Then I'm sure she has\Na very good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:27.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565252,567129}Just mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:31.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567129,571092}I don't want to hear your ideas\Nabout St. Tail's motives!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:36.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:571342,576055}What?! You'll never capture St. Tail,\Nnot in a million years!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:38.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576055,578766}Oh, be quiet!\NYou don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:39.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578766,579850}Oh, yes I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:41.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579850,581393}Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:45.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583062,585523}Yes, I do!\NBecause I'm St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:46.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585940,586899}{\i1}Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:50.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587817,590027}Huh?\NWhat was that about St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:51.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590277,591278}{\i1}Oh no…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:07.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604708,607753}{\i1}Oh, brother,\NI can't believe I said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:14.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609922,614176}Ruby, do you think\NAsuka caught what I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:19.39,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:617429,619390}{\an2\i1}Seika News Station
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:25.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621934,625146}{\i1}Good evening.\NThis is the Seika News Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:28.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625771,628941}{\i1}Our first story this evening features\Nthe city's Christmas Eve festivities…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:31.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628941,631068}{\i1}Hey, you!\NHow'd you get in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:32.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631068,632236}{\i1}You shouldn't be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:37.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634530,637116}Mama, come look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:39.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638242,639618}What is it, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:44.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640786,644373}Isn't that Meimi's classmate on TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:45.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644373,645082}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:47.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644832,647835}{\an8\i1}Give me a break!\NI'll make it quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:48.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645082,648085}See? It's that smart kid.\NThe mayor's pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:51.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648085,651088}You're right.\NI wonder what he's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:51.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651088,651922}Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:53.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652256,653841}{\an8\i1}You grump!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:54.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653841,654925}{\an8\i1}Ow! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:56.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654925,656594}{\an8\i1}Hey! Hey! That's my mic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:58.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656594,658387}{\an8\i1}Hey, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:57.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656135,657595}What is it, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:02.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:659096,662641}{\an8\i1}I have a message for St. Tail!\NMeet me tonight at Park A!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:01.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658637,661640}Look, isn't that boy in your class?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:05.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663225,665144}{\i1}I'll be waiting alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:09.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668230,669857}{\i1}I'm doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:14.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670274,674195}{\i1}If you don't come, I'll reveal\Nyour identity to the entire city!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:20.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676822,680034}{\i1}There's no escaping those eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:23.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680743,683037}{\i1}– Quick! Cut the cameras! Cut!\N– You hear me?! I'll repeat it once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:24.53,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:683078,684538}{\an8}Please Stand By
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:29.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685331,689293}St. Tail, eh?\NI'll bet she's a beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:31.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689293,691003}Just like when you were younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:34.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691378,694256}Hey, I'm still beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696091,697259}Meimi, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:38.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:697801,698761}Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:40.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699845,700846}Huh?
Comment: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:41.72,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:701722,701722}Eyecatch A
Comment: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:47.72,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:707728,707728}Eyecatch B
Comment: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:52.73,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:712733,712733}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:58.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714652,718447}You mustn't go. It's a bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:00.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718447,720908}It might be one of Asuka Jr.'s tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:03.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:722201,723994}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:07.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725579,727623}Do you think I'm crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:11.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729458,731085}If I'm going to be caught,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:15.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731085,735547}I have this funny feeling it'd be better\Nif Asuka was the one to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:17.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:735547,737383}Meimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:737383,739593}Do you think I shouldn't go, Seira?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:25.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:743138,745557}It wouldn't do any good\Nto stop you, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:28.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:746600,748352}But listen, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:31.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:748352,751730}You must never reveal your\Nidentity to him on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:35.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:751730,755109}You must take him by surprise\Nas you've always done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:35.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755109,755943}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:40.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755943,760155}We don't know how much\Nhe really knows, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:45.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761824,765786}Besides, you have\Na job to do tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:46.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765786,766954}I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:766954,768539}Yes, for Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:52.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768956,772584}Oh, that's right.\NI haven't gotten Tama back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:57.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:772584,777423}Poor Mayu. She's been waiting\Nanxiously for Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:13:01.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777423,781010}You're right. But why\Ndoes it have to be tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:05.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:782136,785723}The truth is, Mayu and\Nher family are moving
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:07.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785723,787891}to another city far from here\Ntomorrow, Christmas Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:09.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787891,789560}She's moving away?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:16.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:794231,796650}Mayu, just forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:23.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798610,803157}That's why tonight\Nis the last chance you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:26.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805284,806910}Alright, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:29.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806910,809955}Let's give her an\Nunforgettable Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:31.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810539,811540}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:36.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:813083,816920}Meimi, when the time comes that\Nyou're captured, we'll go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:48.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:825220,828891}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:54.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833771,834897}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:58.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837358,838567}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:02.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840402,842488}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:21.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858087,861882}May the blessings of God be with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:35.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:872518,875187}Maybe she wasn't watching TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:42.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881068,882778}Snow…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:45.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883570,885656}It's going to be a white Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:48.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885656,888242}Brr… it's freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:55.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894164,895916}Well, I guess\Nshe's not going to show.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:18.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:916270,918772}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:19.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:918772,919898}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:28.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924987,928615}You must take him by surprise,\Nas you've always done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:33.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931285,933871}I don't know what good it'll do but…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:40.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:937124,940419}It's Show Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:46.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:945674,946884}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:51.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949136,951346}Will you stop?\NI've had enough of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:57.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:954600,957436}Why do you think\NI left that cell phone over there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:02.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958645,962816}Listen! I'm not leaving here,\Nso you can just relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:05.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:964026,965194}Did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:10.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965194,970032}Yes! But you said\Nyou'd reveal my identity…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:11.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970032,971533}It was a bluff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:14.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972868,974745}{\i1}Oh, brother.\NHe doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:18.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974745,978165}{\i1}Never mind that.\NWhy didn't you send me a note?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:19.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978165,979625}{\i1}How do I explain?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:23.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979625,983003}Is that why you called me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:25.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983003,985506}{\i1}This is very important, so listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:29.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986131,989468}You know what it means if you don't\Nlet me know where you're going to strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:31.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989468,991470}It means I won't be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:34.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992638,994473}{\i1}And that means… um…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:37.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994848,997267}Err, let's put it this way…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:41.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998894,1001188}What'll happen if\Nsomebody else captures you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:43.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002898,1003690}{\i1}I mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:47.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005108,1007152}{\i1}What are you saying, stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:48.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007152,1008612}{\i1}I…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:49.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008612,1009154}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:50.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009571,1010656}I'm coming over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:56.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015202,1016828}{\i1}Forgive me, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:17:01.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018080,1021458}You must never reveal\Nyour identity to him on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:04.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022584,1024378}{\i1}But… I…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:10.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027798,1030384}Darn, the glass is\Nso fogged up, I can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:18.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036431,1038100}St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:25.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044731,1045524}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:29.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047109,1049278}Uh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:31.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050153,1051405}My promise…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:35.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053115,1055617}I'm sorry I broke my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:38.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057286,1058745}I'll never do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:39.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058745,1059705}Yeah. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:42.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061373,1062499}That's why…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:45.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063917,1065002}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:47.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066086,1067129}That's why…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:50.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068171,1070966}{\i1}I don't want you to give up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:53.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071508,1073719}I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:56.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075012,1076179}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:17:59.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077347,1079683}Don't get caught\Nuntil I catch up with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:01.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080767,1081852}Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:05.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082936,1085772}It's a promise!\NDon't you forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:09.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089109,1089776}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:32.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107002,1112424}"I am going to the Ogasawara residence\Nthis evening to take their pet, Tama – St. Tail".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:36.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112841,1116178}Tonight?!\NI don't have much time left!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:38.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117763,1118930}Darn her!
